---
// Compliance.astro - Componente rediseñado para la normatividad
---

<section id="normativa" class="norm-section">
  <div class="norm-container">
    <div class="norm-header">
      <h2>Normatividad y Cumplimiento Legal</h2>
      <p>Operamos bajo los más altos estándares regulatorios para garantizar la calidad y seguridad alimentaria en todos nuestros procesos.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="norm-main-card">
      <div class="norm-decree-badge">
        <span class="norm-decree-number">1500</span>
        <span class="norm-decree-year">2007</span>
      </div>
      
      <div class="norm-content">
        <div class="norm-title-row">
          <h3>Decreto 1500 de 2007</h3>
          <div class="norm-plant-code">
            <span>CÓDIGO DE PLANTA</span>
            <strong>266B</strong>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <p class="norm-description">
          El Decreto 1500 establece el reglamento técnico que crea el Sistema Oficial de Inspección, Vigilancia y Control de la Carne, Productos Cárnicos Comestibles y Derivados Cárnicos Destinados para el Consumo Humano. Este decreto nos permite beneficiar cualquier animal y transportarlo a nivel nacional bajo estrictas normas de calidad.
        </p>
        
        <div class="norm-pillars">
          <div class="norm-pillar">
            <div class="norm-pillar-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="norm-pillar-content">
              <h4>Sanidad e Inocuidad</h4>
              <p>Implementamos todos los requisitos sanitarios y de inocuidad establecidos para garantizar la calidad y seguridad de nuestros productos.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="norm-pillar">
            <div class="norm-pillar-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 11c0 3.517-1.009 6.799-2.753 9.571m-3.44-2.04l.054-.09A13.916 13.916 0 008 11a4 4 0 118 0c0 1.017-.07 2.019-.203 3m-2.118 6.844A21.88 21.88 0 0015.171 17m3.839 1.132c.645-2.266.99-4.659.99-7.132A8 8 0 008 4.07M3 15.364c.64-1.319 1-2.8 1-4.364 0-1.457.39-2.823 1.07-4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="norm-pillar-content">
              <h4>Bienestar Animal</h4>
              <p>Aplicamos todas las normativas relacionadas con el bienestar animal desde la recepción hasta el proceso de sacrificio.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="norm-pillar">
            <div class="norm-pillar-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="norm-pillar-content">
              <h4>Trazabilidad</h4>
              <p>Contamos con sistemas de trazabilidad que cumplen con los requisitos establecidos por la normativa, permitiendo un seguimiento completo.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="norm-pillar">
            <div class="norm-pillar-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="norm-pillar-content">
              <h4>Instalaciones</h4>
              <p>Nuestras instalaciones están diseñadas y equipadas según los estándares requeridos por la legislación para garantizar procesos óptimos.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="norm-cards">
      <div class="norm-card-commitment">
        <div class="norm-card-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Compromiso con la mejora continua</h3>
        <p>En Frigorinoquia no solo nos limitamos a cumplir con las normativas vigentes, sino que trabajamos constantemente en la mejora de nuestros procesos, buscando superar los estándares establecidos y anticipándonos a futuras regulaciones.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="norm-card-inspection">
        <div class="norm-card-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Inspección Constante</h3>
        <p>Nuestras instalaciones y procesos están bajo supervisión constante por parte de inspectores oficiales que garantizan el cumplimiento de todas las normativas vigentes.</p>
        <div class="norm-info-row">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="norm-info-icon" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
          <p>Contamos con un sistema de gestión que nos permite mantener actualizados nuestros procesos conforme a las nuevas regulaciones.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="norm-banner">
      <div class="norm-banner-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16H9m3 0h3" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="norm-banner-content">
        <h3>Garantía de Cumplimiento Legal</h3>
        <p>Al elegir a Frigorinoquia, usted tiene la seguridad de trabajar con una planta que cumple rigurosamente con todas las normativas nacionales, permitiendo la comercialización legal de sus productos a nivel nacional.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Estilos base de la sección */
  .norm-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background-color: #F9FAFB;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .norm-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 5px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #1E3A8A, #3B82F6);
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .norm-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }
  
  /* Encabezado de sección */
  .norm-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .norm-header h2 {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1E3A8A;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  
  .norm-header h2::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -0.75rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 60px;
    height: 3px;
    background-color: #F97316;
  }
  
  .norm-header p {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: #4B5563;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
  }
  
  /* Tarjeta principal del decreto */
  .norm-main-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: normFadeIn 0.8s ease forwards;
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .norm-main-card {
      flex-direction: row;
    }
  }
  
  /* Badge del decreto */
  .norm-decree-badge {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E3A8A, #2563EB);
    color: white;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .norm-decree-badge {
      min-width: 180px;
    }
  }
  
  .norm-decree-badge::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    left: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 60%);
  }
  
  .norm-decree-number {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .norm-decree-year {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.25rem 1rem;
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 9999px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  /* Contenido del decreto */
  .norm-content {
    padding: 2.5rem;
    flex: 1;
  }
  
  /* Fila del título */
  .norm-title-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .norm-title-row {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
  
  .norm-title-row h3 {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1E3A8A;
    position: relative;
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  .norm-title-row h3::after {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 40px;
    height: 2px;
    background-color: #F97316;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  /* Código de planta */
  .norm-plant-code {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: #F3F4F6;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border: 2px dashed #D1D5DB;
  }
  
  .norm-plant-code span {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #4B5563;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  
  .norm-plant-code strong {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1E3A8A;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  
  /* Descripción del decreto */
  .norm-description {
    color: #4B5563;
    font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  /* Pilares de cumplimiento */
  .norm-pillars {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .norm-pillars {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
  
  /* Pilar individual */
  .norm-pillar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background-color: #F9FAFB;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    border-left: 4px solid #1E3A8A;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .norm-pillar:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }
  
  .norm-pillar-icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    min-width: 40px;
    background-color: rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.1);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #1E3A8A;
  }
  
  .norm-pillar-icon svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
  }
  
  .norm-pillar-content h4 {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1E3A8A;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
  }
  
  .norm-pillar-content p {
    color: #4B5563;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  /* Tarjetas secundarias */
  .norm-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .norm-cards {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
  
  /* Tarjeta de compromiso */
  .norm-card-commitment {
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-top: 5px solid #F97316;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: normFadeIn 0.8s ease forwards 0.2s;
  }
  
  .norm-card-commitment::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: 150px;
    height: 150px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.1) 0%, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0) 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    transform: translate(30%, -30%);
    z-index: 0;
  }
  
  /* Tarjeta de inspección */
  .norm-card-inspection {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E3A8A, #2563EB);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    color: white;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: normFadeIn 0.8s ease forwards 0.4s;
  }
  
  .norm-card-inspection::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    transform: translate(30%, -30%);
    z-index: 0;
  }
  
  /* Estilos compartidos para las tarjetas */
  .norm-card-icon {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .norm-card-commitment .norm-card-icon {
    background-color: rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.1);
    color: #F97316;
  }
  
  .norm-card-icon svg {
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
  }
  
  .norm-card-commitment h3,
  .norm-card-inspection h3 {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .norm-card-commitment h3 {
    color: #111827;
  }
  
  .norm-card-commitment p,
  .norm-card-inspection p {
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
  }
  
  .norm-card-commitment p {
    color: #4B5563;
  }
  
  .norm-card-inspection p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }
  
  /* Fila de información */
  .norm-info-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .norm-info-icon {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    min-width: 20px;
    color: white;
  }
  
  .norm-info-row p {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  /* Banner de garantía */
  .norm-banner {
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: normFadeIn 0.8s ease forwards 0.6s;
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .norm-banner {
      flex-direction: row;
    }
  }
  
  .norm-banner::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 5px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #1E3A8A, #3B82F6);
  }
  
  .norm-banner-icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E3A8A, #2563EB);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .norm-banner-icon svg {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    color: white;
  }
  
  .norm-banner-content h3 {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1E3A8A;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .norm-banner-content p {
    color: #4B5563;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
  }
  
  /* Animaciones */
  @keyframes normFadeIn {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
  
  /* Media queries adicionales */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .norm-section {
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }
    
    .norm-header h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .norm-content {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .norm-title-row h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .norm-decree-number {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }
    
    .norm-decree-year {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
    
    .norm-card-commitment,
    .norm-card-inspection {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .norm-banner {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .norm-banner-content h3 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  // Script para activar animaciones cuando los elementos entran en el viewport
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          (entry.target as HTMLElement).style.animationPlayState = 'running';
          observer.unobserve(entry.target);
        }
      });
    }, {
      threshold: 0.1
    });
    
    const animatedElements = document.querySelectorAll('.norm-main-card, .norm-card-commitment, .norm-card-inspection, .norm-banner');
    animatedElements.forEach(el => {
      (el as HTMLElement).style.animationPlayState = 'paused';
      observer.observe(el);
    });
  });
</script>